    <article class="classe-exercise">
      <div class="exercise-head">
        <span class="num">37</span>
        <span class="ttl">Equacions irracionals més complicades (dues o tres arrels)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="statement-wrap">
        <p class="note">Comprova amb GeoGebra els resultats que has obtingut.</p><ol class="apartados">
<li><span class="letter">a)</span> <span class="stmt">$x + \sqrt{x+1} - 2x = 1$</span></li>
<li><span class="letter">b)</span> <span class="stmt">$\sqrt{x-3} + \sqrt{x+4} = \sqrt{4x+1}$</span></li>
<li><span class="letter">c)</span> <span class="stmt">$x - \sqrt{x^{2}-3} = \sqrt{x-1}$</span></li>
<li><span class="letter">d)</span> <span class="stmt">$\sqrt{x} + \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{x}} = \dfrac{x+1}{2}$</span></li>
</ol>
      </div>

      <button class="solution-toggle" data-toggles="sol-37" data-show-label="Mostra la solució" data-hide-label="Amaga la solució" onclick="toggleSolucion('sol-37')">
        <span class="toggle-label">Mostra la solució</span>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>

      <section class="classe-solution" id="sol-37" hidden>
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.6rem;font-size:1rem">Solució pas a pas</h3>
        <div class="apartado-sol"><h4><span class="letter">a)</span> <span class="stmt">$x + \sqrt{x+1} - 2x = 1$</span></h4><p>Simplifiquem: $\;-x + \sqrt{x+1} = 1 \;\Rightarrow\; \sqrt{x+1} = x + 1$. Elevem al quadrat:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$x + 1 = (x+1)^{2}.$$</div>
              <p>Sigui $u = x+1$: $\;u = u^{2} \Rightarrow u(u-1) = 0 \Rightarrow u = 0$ o $u = 1$. Així $\,x = -1$ o $\,x = 0$.</p>
              <p><strong>Verificació:</strong> $x=-1$: $\;-1 + \sqrt{0} - (-2) = -1 + 0 + 2 = 1$ ✓. &nbsp;$x=0$: $\;0 + \sqrt{1} - 0 = 1$ ✓.</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$\boxed{\;x = -1\ \text{o}\ x = 0.\;}$$</div></div>
<div class="apartado-sol"><h4><span class="letter">b)</span> <span class="stmt">$\sqrt{x-3} + \sqrt{x+4} = \sqrt{4x+1}$</span></h4><p>Elevem al quadrat directament:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$(x-3) + 2\sqrt{(x-3)(x+4)} + (x+4) = 4x + 1.$$</div>
              <p>Aïllem l'arrel: $\;2\sqrt{(x-3)(x+4)} = 4x + 1 - 2x - 1 = 2x \;\Rightarrow\; \sqrt{(x-3)(x+4)} = x$. Elevem al quadrat:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$(x-3)(x+4) = x^{2} \;\Longrightarrow\; x^{2} + x - 12 = x^{2} \;\Longrightarrow\; x = 12.$$</div>
              <p><strong>Verificació:</strong> $\;\sqrt{9} + \sqrt{16} = 3 + 4 = 7 = \sqrt{49}$ ✓.</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$\boxed{\;x = 12.\;}$$</div></div>
<div class="apartado-sol"><h4><span class="letter">c)</span> <span class="stmt">$x - \sqrt{x^{2}-3} = \sqrt{x-1}$</span></h4><p>Elevem al quadrat:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$\bigl(x - \sqrt{x^{2}-3}\bigr)^{2} = x - 1 \;\Longrightarrow\; x^{2} - 2x\sqrt{x^{2}-3} + (x^{2}-3) = x - 1.$$</div>
              <p>Aïllem l'arrel: $\;2x^{2} - 3 - x + 1 = 2x\sqrt{x^{2}-3} \;\Rightarrow\; 2x^{2} - x - 2 = 2x\sqrt{x^{2}-3}$. Elevem al quadrat:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$(2x^{2} - x - 2)^{2} = 4x^{2}(x^{2} - 3).$$</div>
              <div class="math-block">$$4x^{4} - 4x^{3} - 7x^{2} + 4x + 4 = 4x^{4} - 12x^{2}.$$</div>
              <div class="math-block">$$0 = 4x^{3} - 5x^{2} - 4x - 4.$$</div>
              <p>Per Ruffini provem $x = 2$: $\,32 - 20 - 8 - 4 = 0$ ✓. Llavors $\,4x^{3} - 5x^{2} - 4x - 4 = (x-2)(4x^{2} + 3x + 2)$, i la quadràtica té $\Delta = 9 - 32 < 0$, sense més arrels reals.</p>
              <p><strong>Verificació:</strong> $x = 2$: $\;2 - \sqrt{1} = 1 = \sqrt{1}$ ✓.</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$\boxed{\;x = 2.\;}$$</div></div>
<div class="apartado-sol"><h4><span class="letter">d)</span> <span class="stmt">$\sqrt{x} + \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{x}} = \dfrac{x+1}{2}$</span></h4><p>Multipliquem tot per $\,2\sqrt{x}\,$ (condició $x > 0$):</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$2x + 2 = \sqrt{x}\,(x+1).$$</div>
              <p>Elevem al quadrat:</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$(2x+2)^{2} = x\,(x+1)^{2} \;\Longrightarrow\; 4x^{2} + 8x + 4 = x^{3} + 2x^{2} + x.$$</div>
              <div class="math-block">$$0 = x^{3} - 2x^{2} - 7x - 4.$$</div>
              <p>Per Ruffini provem $x = 4$: $\,64 - 32 - 28 - 4 = 0$ ✓. Llavors $\,x^{3} - 2x^{2} - 7x - 4 = (x-4)(x^{2} + 2x + 1) = (x-4)(x+1)^{2}$. Candidats: $x = 4$ i $x = -1$ (doble).</p>
              <p><strong>Verificació:</strong> $x = -1$: $\sqrt{-1}$ no està definit → descarta. &nbsp;$x = 4$: $\;\sqrt{4} + \tfrac{1}{\sqrt{4}} = 2 + \tfrac{1}{2} = \tfrac{5}{2} = \tfrac{4+1}{2}$ ✓.</p>
              <div class="math-block">$$\boxed{\;x = 4.\;}$$</div></div>
      </section>

